	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I was playing Hoyle card games yesterday and wondered how do I play gameboy color only( Clear carts) on a standard gameboy. is there a gg code for this or some kind of solution to the problem caus' my brother asked me and I don't really know.

		

		</td>
